DocAttribute.Name: ReferencedDocument
DocAttribute.Documentation: A document such as a price list or quotation from which costs are obtained.

DocAttribute.Name: ReferencingValues
DocAttribute.Documentation: Costs obtained from a single document such as a price list or quotation.

DocAttribute.Name: Name
DocAttribute.Documentation: A name used to identify or qualify the relationship to the document from which values may be referenced..

DocAttribute.Name: Description
DocAttribute.Documentation: A description of the relationship to the document from which values may be referenced.
